Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.35,0:00:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.84,0:00:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.30,0:00:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:01:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.38,0:01:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.36,0:01:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Eternal Wall - God Slime!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It sent my Obelisk's attack\N right back at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik's Wall Monster has taken on the ability of immortality!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He plans to use\N the God Slime as a wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and wait for a card that can allow him to resurrect Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And every attack I send his way only damages {\b0}me{\b1} instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And in turn causes my partner to be consumed by the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But we won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chances are born\N from the depths of a pinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:02:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Obelisk's Anger -\N Soul Energy MAX"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a close look!\N Resurrection of the Dead\N has returned to my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.85,0:02:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm pretty sure you know\N what that means by {\i1}now{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can Special Summon Ra\N on my next turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness of Hell is {\i1}finally{\i0}\N here to take you away, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as Malik has the God Slime protecting him on the field, I can't beat any of his Monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The {\b0}real{\b1} wall\N blocking my path right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is the one being held as a sacrifice,\N Malik's dominant personality!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I defeat Malik's dark personality,\N his original personality will die...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I place a reverse card...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I Summon {\i1}this{\i0} guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granadora in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as this creature stays\N on my field in Defense Position,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}my Life will increase by\N 1000 points every turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That will cover the cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And next turn, God will rise as a phoenix\N and burn Obelisk to ashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And once Obelisk is gone, Yugi...\N you have no chance of winning...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My... turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he doesn't stop him this turn, he's going to Summon Ra {\i1}next{\i0} turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Yugi's acting like there's something\N holding him back in this Duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding him back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's like he's pulling his punches and holding back his attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.\N You guys can't see it, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Malik again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't aware that these two are\N fighting a Dark Game with one another\N up atop that Duel Ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of fight is it this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:04:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it like when he played me and I felt\N the pain my Monsters felt, Malik?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of them have another self.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They fight with both myself and Yugi,\N their other personalities,\N as human sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other Yugi's\N being held as the sacrifice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When one of their \NLife Points reaches zero,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the sacrifice will fall \Ninto eternal darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That includes the fragment of myself \NI placed inside of Anzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal darkness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what do you mean by,\N "fall into eternal darkness"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Was I saying something just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi acts like he doesn't\N want to take my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Long before any of this,\N I was trying to take the lives\N of you and your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\b0}Me{\b1}, not {\b0}him{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So {\b0}why{\b1}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our real enemy is Malik's evil side!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There has to be a way to\N defeat him and him alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But how should we fight then...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if his Life Points reach zero,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik's good side is\N the one that will die...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His evil side will stay alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe his weakness\N is tied to Ra's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ra's power?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah. Ra has three modes\N of battle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And one of those is the ability\N of Ra to fuse with the player!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But even "God" is merely a Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that means, if they fuse,\N the player becomes a Monster too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The player becomes a Monster...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you, Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:05:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There may still be a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set two reverse cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Summon Illusion Beast Gazelle\N in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa there! Don't forget\N that this guy gets an attack\N on the end of your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bowganian!\N Release the Crossbow of Pain on Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please do it!\N Defeat Malik's evil heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner, I won't let you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter {\i1}what{\i0} you say,\N this is going to be the last turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On this turn, he'll bring back Ra\N with Resurrection of the Dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, do you have\N any way to stop him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:06:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness is \Nmy ally 'till the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this card, I'm {\i1}guaranteed{\i0}\N to offer you to the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And on my Standby Phase,\N Granadora's Effect activates and\N increases my Life Points by 1000!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll burn to death in one sweep\N of the Sun God's wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resurrection of the Dead!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Phoenix...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I give up 1000 of my Life Points\N in order to activate Ra's third Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn Obelisk to ashes!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Phoenix!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing you do will matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obelisk is dea-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Osiris the Heaven Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Osiris is {\b0}shielding{\b1} Obelisk\N from the God Phoenix?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment you attacked,\N I used {\b0}my{\b1} reverse card!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resurrection of the Dead,\N one you know well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So on this turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obelisk is unharmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! It's not like Malik's \Nthe only one who has\N Resurrection of the Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Osiris acted as a Monster shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To challenge Ra with Obelisk as\N a sword and Osiris as a shield...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obelisk... is mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi... You know...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That anger is what unleashes\N Obelisk's {\b0}true{\b1} power...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The phoenix... shall return to\N the Graveyard once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think\N this means you've won, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Battle Phase is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He ended his Battle Phase\N without attacking? What's he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't mean my turn is {\i1}over{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That this turn will be the {\i1}last{\i0} turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprise Attack from the Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprise Attack from the Darkness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, \NI get an entire second Battle Phase!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can revive the Monster\N Summoned in this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:09:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Another{\i0} Battle Phase?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That card can't be legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik, you fiend...\N Are you going to Special Summon Ra\N all over again and finish Yugi off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord... Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth!\N The Winged Sun Dragon of Ra!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here it comes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now{\i0} then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ra is still not in Battle Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What form shall I attack you with?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of {\i1}course{\i0}, I'll use {\i1}this{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's Ra's second form!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik's going to fuse\N with Ra for a One Turn Kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik is left with one Life Point,\N and all the rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...are transferred to\N Ra's Attack Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, Partner! I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's now or never!\N It's our last chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch as I become one with Ra!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In this one moment, we can beat Malik's\N dark side and Ra at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... If I sacrifice all the\N Monsters on my field,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ra's Attack Points will rise to 6899!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Far{\i0} beyond your Obelisk's\N mere {\i1}4000{\i0} Attack Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can blast your Life Points\N to 0 in one shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brace{\i0} yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh... We'll {\i1}see{\i0} about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the moment your evil heart\N manifests in the form of a beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:12:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Taker!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, what's that card?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Taker...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Magic Card that lets you\N sacrifice one Monster on the\N opponent's side of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time,\N the opponent gains 1000 Life Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me, Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical effects only work for\N one turn against gods...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to\N sacrifice me along with Ra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! He's sacrificing Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With this method,\N because the player\N has one Life Point left...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The real Malik, the human sacrifice,\N won't have to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you {\i1}really{\i0} think you could\N destroy {\i1}me{\i0} by sacrificing Ra!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh! And who said\N I was sacrificing {\i1}Ra{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who's he sacrificing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sacrifice...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is right {\i1}there{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sacrificing... God Slime?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... Your God Slime is\N merely a fusion of Revival Slime\N and Reflect Slime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm able to count it as {\i1}two{\i0} sacrifices\N for the price of {\i1}one{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! What do you\N hope to accomplish by\N sacrificing my Slime?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's to activate\N Obelisk's {\i1}greatest{\i0} Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obelisk's greatest Ability?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Energy MAX!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Soul Energy MAX...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}God's pent up anger\N will create a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is Obelisk's greatest Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But will it work against Ra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Attack Power is {\i1}infinite{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go, Malik!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Hand Impact!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This moment, I take the\N Monsters on my field...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bowganian and Granadora!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And offer them up to Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Soul Taker was activated, Malik received 1000 Life Points, which were in turn added to Ra's Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So Ra has 1699 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Additionally, adding the Attack Points\N of the Monsters he sacrificed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ra will grow even more powerful...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ra now has 4899 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Obelisk has infinite Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should be able to beat Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did it work...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he still standing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I activated this Magic Card...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class System?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When our Monsters engage in battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if the Level of my opponent's Monster\N is equal to or less than my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that Monster's Attack Power \Nand Effects are negated!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ra and Obelisk both\N have a Level of ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there you have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obelisk's Effect has been\N rendered useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad for {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the Effect wears off,\N Obelisk's Attack Points return to 4000.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi's... going to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now! \NSurprise Attack from the Darkness!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the final Battle Phase!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lord... Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You mustn't... make this mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ra attacks you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Blaze Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse Magic, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Dimension!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Magic activates when my opponent\N attacks while I control a\N Spellcaster on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Dimension sacrifices two\N of the Monsters on my field!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You're sacrificing {\i1}God{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:18:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By sacrificing Obelisk and Gazelle,\N Ra's attack has been evaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrifice Escape!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I heard it back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The voice of Lord Malik's soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rishid...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon I'll be\N headed to the Dark World...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I do, there's something\N I want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I disobeyed the laws of my clan\N and committed a terrible sin...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal darkness isn't enough to\N punish me for what I did to Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now that you've lost {\i1}God{\i0},\N do you really think you have\N any hope of {\i1}defeating{\i0} me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the servants, my {\i1}comrades{\i0},\N who have been fighting\N alongside me in my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now for\N Magical Dimension's {\i1}other{\i0} effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am able to Special Summon one\N Spellcaster-Type Monster from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So Obelisk was just a decoy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This turn, we will counterattack Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ragnarok!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card can only be activated if I have\N at least two Magician Monsters on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remove all the Monsters in my deck,\N Graveyard and on the field from play!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By doing so, I can destroy every\N Monster my opponent controls!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That includes {\i1}you{\i0},  a fusion between\N God and yourself, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However{\i0}, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you destroy Ra, you will leave me\N with only 1 Life Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can tell you right now that my dominant personality
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:20:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hardly has enough life energy\N to live on one measly Life Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By destroying {\i1}Ra{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'd be snuffing the life\N of my dominant half in the {\i1}process{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he saying that even if\N I leave one Life Point,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't save Malik!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rishid...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I went through\N the Ritual of the Tomb Guardians,\N you endured the same pain I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made a choice then to\N share my sin and share my destiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You decided to live\N with me in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And yet, you've done enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But there's no need for you\N to suffer anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! If you're prepared to\N {\i1}kill{\i0} him, go ahead and {\i1}try{\i0} it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way!\N Now my other self can't attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as I have this sacrifice,\N I can't {\i1}lose{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether I live or die...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the outcome,\N you need to keep heading toward the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is... not right... Lord Malik...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you... Rishid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Malik!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rishid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rishid...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that man Rishid-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was lying\N in the Battle Ship unconscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:22:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when Rishid-{\i1}san{\i0} begins speaking, Malik's face begins to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.84,0:22:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik's dominant personality\N is beginning to awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Betting his life on one point, Yugi goes on the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle City finally reaches its climax!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.76,0:22:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can Yugi beat Malik's dark personality and save everyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.39,0:22:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The End of Battle City!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.18,0:22:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.54,0:22:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.15,0:22:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.22,0:23:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.70,0:23:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.98,0:23:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.88,0:23:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.03,0:23:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.55,0:23:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
